{"tid":1747072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港人 咪撚再輸】聽日 係香港關鍵嘅一日","createTime":"2019-11-23T04:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:57:38.000Z","uid":257683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f92841e9a2ada6cbdebcee947191a0e14fd0d0","tid":1747072,"uid":257683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"有票嘅你一定要投<br />\n<br />\n老實講 唔係話好中意泛民 <br />\n<br />\n但再比建制贏嘅話我地只會輸多一仗<br />\n<br />\n呢個亦係暫時我地唯一可以係政制內做到嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n最低限到要令更多非建制面孔進駐區議會<br />\n<br />\n改變建制佔大多數嘅局面<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb214bac93afada2707e0a3b975fcde0ab67665b","tid":1747072,"uid":257683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a1f2923a44d8c9e6ff6a650240402e595e6726","tid":1747072,"uid":257683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}